TestCase Scenario:
Verify search button
by entring valid data
in respective fields
Testcase Description:
This test case validates
login functionality with
valid data
Steps Description:
Enter valid url in the search
button and click on ok

Test data:
FROM
TO
DATE//MONTH//YEAR
ALL CLASSES
GENERAL
Steps Description:
1.Enter valid FROM data
2.Enter valid TO data
3.select valid DATE//MONTH//YEAR
4.Select valid ALL CLASSES
5.Select valid GENERAL
6.Click on SEARCH button
